name: Cowbell Hero for iOS and Playstation Vita
blurb: This is the music game you have all been waiting for. Play the cowbell to 26 Songs including the hit "(Don't Fear) The Reaper".

rewards.reward: Digital Download of the Original Soundtrack\r\n=============================The 15 original songs from the game remastered and available to download.

Digital Download of Soundtrack and Comic Book
=============================
The 15 original songs from the game remastered and available to download.

The comic adaptation available as a pdf download.

Printed 48 page Comic Book - Standard Cover\r\n=============================\r\nThe physical printing of the comic adaptation. A 48 page book that includes additional artwork for the "disco showdown" and the "battle with death". Digital download of the comic is also included.

Physical CD of the Original Soundtrack
=============================
The 15 original songs from the game remastered and presented in a professionally printed digipack case with screen printed CD. Includes the songs:
“Cowbell Blues”, “Funkify”, “Give and Take”, “More Cowbell”, “Annabelle”, “Kung Fu Fro”, “Wacky Tobacky”, “More Cowbell (Remix)”, “Wobble Funk”, 
“Bass Bell”, “Cowbell Duel”, “Ohm”, “DNB Bell”, “Mad Cowbell Disease”, “More Cowbell (Dubstep)”

Cowbell Hero iPhone Case\r\n=============================\r\nThe official Cowbell Hero iPhone case. Case is available in either iPhone 4 or iPhone 5 sizes. It has a full color printed back and clear sides.
Cowbell Hero T-Shirt\r\n=============================\r\nThe official Cowbell Hero T-Shirt. Features the logo and tagline "One Man, One Dream, More Cowbell"

Playstation Vita Case and Manual\r\n============================= Limited edition Playstation Vita game case with full color insert and instruction manual. This physical game case is for the die hard collectors out there. Cowbell Hero game not included. Game will only be available via download.

Comic Book, Soundtrack CD, Mini Poster, Sticker\r\n=============================\r\nThe printed comic book with standard cover, the physical CD soundtrack, the Cowbell Hero poster (comic book sized), and an app icon sticker. Digital download of the comic is also included.
High Quality Large Poster 24"x36"\r\n=============================\r\nThe Cowbell Hero poster in a full 24"x36" high quality print. Item will ship rolled in a tube.

Comic Book, Soundtrack CD, iPhone Case, Mini Poster, Sticker\r\n=============================\r\nThe printed comic book with standard cover, the physical CD soundtrack, iPhone case, the Cowbell Hero poster (comic book sized), and an app icon sticker. Digital download of the comic is also included.

Digital download of the comic is also included.

Comic Book Alternate Cover, Comic Book Standard Cover, Soundtrack CD, iPhone Case, T-Shirt, Mini Poster, Sticker, Swag Bag\r\n==============================\r\nA limited printing alternate cover of the comic book (signed and numbered) plus one copy of the standard cover of the comic book, physical CD soundtrack, iPhone case, T-Shirt, the Cowbell Hero poster (comic book sized), and an app icon sticker. Digital download of the comic is also included. Plus a cloth swag bag printed with the Cowbell Hero logo.

Digital download of the comic is also included. Plus a cloth swag bag printed with the Cowbell Hero logo. Plus the Cowbell Hero poster in a full 24"x36" high quality print. Item will ship rolled in a tube.

The Cowbell Hero Arcade Experience!\r\n==============================\r\nA custom built Cowbell Hero arcade style cabinet. It is a hand built Oak Cabinet. Metal iPad enclosure with lock. Backlit artwork behind iPad and backlit marquee. Sony speakers with sub. Removable back door with lock. Inside of cabinet signed by the game's (and cabinet's) creator David Corrigan. A professional cabinet all the way. Also includes a new 16GB Black WiFi iPad with Retina Display ($499 value). Just plug it in and enjoy Cowbell Hero  the way it was meant to be played! Shipped door to door via freight company. $250 of shipping in the continental US included. Also includes all the swag from the $100 pledge. Not available to backers outside the US.
